race.comment: DEEP STEALTH (3) nice mare who should be able to finally break through this preparation, fifth-up. Tagged the speed as the ($1.50 fav) when she gave her all for a brave third over 1175m at Grafton. D-Day is looming. PER CAPITA (6) resumes with excellent fresh credentials. Proven at this course and distance and wasn't pushed out in his 946m trial. Now in the Stephen Lee yard and has a key jockey change. VETOED (7) has finished in the minor money at her last four starts and is desperately close to breaking through. Deep into the prep and brings the right set of figures to take this out. BETTER NOT BITTER (8) trained locally and returned to form in the heavy conditions when a game winner over 1255m here. Gets in light again with the claim. Sure to be thereabouts.
